node.text:
Happy Happy Hour! The best accessory is a smile - and it's best paired with the voice behind it. On today's Happy Hour At Home, Katie Grossbard of @iamavoter walks us through the four ways you can vote this year, and answers some common FAQs about mail-in ballots. 

Remember, our democracy works best when we all participate - so make your voting plan now! And don't forget - 10% of the proceeds of our I Vote Necklace (that Katie is wearing here!) go to @iamavoter.

OddFellows is currently open in NYC at their DUMBO location Fridays-Sundays, and at their Chestnut Hill location Thursday-Sundays, with full hours coming soon!
